Adherence To AI Agent Coding Best Practice Instructions: Act as a senior programmer analyzing the code in a TypeScript application where the content of each file in the application's codebase is shown below in a code block. The file `.cursor/rules/project.mdc` captures coding best practices for coding the project. Review all the code in the codebase and identify the critical places in the code which do not adhere to the rules laid out in the file `.cursor/rules/project.mdc`, outlining the particular point of violation, why it is a violation and what the recommended fix is. Provide references to the specific part(s) of the code that needs these improvements with suggestions on how to improve. Include the list or relative file paths of each source file affected.
